### Base URL — override per environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Replace this variable with an idOperacaoCredito returned by a POST in contratar.http
@idOperacaoCredito = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
###  GET — Query a credit operation by ID
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Fetch an existing operation → 200 OK
###   Response includes all contract fields + idOperacaoCredito + dataContratacao
GET {{baseUrl}}/operacoes-credito/{{idOperacaoCredito}}

###

### Operation not found → 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/operacoes-credito/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
